<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[الازْمِخْرار]</span>: ازْمَخَرَّ الصوت،<span class="c5"> بالخاء معجمة:</span> أي اشتد.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>هرّ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[الازْمِهْرار]</span>: ازْمَهَرَّت عيناه من الغضب: إِذا احمرتا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">وازْمَهَرَّت الكواكب:</span> إِذا لمحت <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[ءك]</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
